# Changelog #

## Version 1.0.3 ##

* Set up CI
* Set up Heroku autodeployment on master branch

These changes will make this repository easier to maintain.

## Version 1.0.2 ##

* Lots of XSS fixes, holy crap
* Moved HTML escaping to before-save, instead of before-render
* Forms are now validated way more thoroughly (Thanks ActiveModel!)

## Version 1.0.1 ##

* Adapted more to Heroku-style development
* Added a procfile, made launching compatible with Foreman
* Vagrantfile also forwards the Foreman port (5000) now

## Version 1.0.0: Initial Release (13 June 2015) ##

* Deployed to Heroku
* Added Heroku cruft
* Made a bunch of config options into environment variables
* Information is passed to the user with flashes (`Rack::Flash`)
* Immediate bugs are patched
